      <description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/paul_graham/essays_zh/word/&#34;&gt;中文版&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://www.paulgraham.com/word.html&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://www.paulgraham.com/word.html&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://www.paulgraham.com/word.html&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;a-word-to-the-resourceful&#34;&gt;A Word to the Resourceful&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;January 2012&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A year ago I noticed a pattern in the least successful startups we&amp;rsquo;d funded: they all seemed hard to talk to. It felt as if there was some kind of wall between us. I could never quite tell if they understood what I was saying.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
